{"tid":684851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"繼高鐵後再取消800億捷運項目 大馬人捐錢償還國債","createTime":"2018-05-31T02:28:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T15:11:31.000Z","uid":26424,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"678c28b93201cdf0026fc2efbd5f29553cf12fdd","tid":684851,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:28:47.000Z","msg":"首相敦馬哈迪表示，政府取消預計耗資400億令吉的捷運三號線（MRT3）項目。<br />\n<br />\n他今日主持第二次的內閣會議後，向記者說：&ldquo;MRT3項目將停止。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這是繼上周宣布取消1100億令吉，全長350公里的馬新高鐵（HSR）項目，以作為削減政府超過1兆令吉債務的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n敦馬曾說過，馬新高鐵項目是不必要的，且不會為國家賺取一分錢。<br />\n<br />\n至於由中國鐵建建設，總值550億令吉、全長600公里的東海岸銜接鐵路，敦馬稱：&ldquo;該項目尚未取消，我們仍在研究此事。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>民眾可透過馬來亞銀行捐款予&ldquo;馬來西亞希望基金會&rdquo;，帳號為566010626452</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8645bc2f37aa901886e0fbc583bed496e56898f5","tid":684851,"uid":92498,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:31:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99cef6f0546564cbc49a99fef2617a7a166b0108","tid":684851,"uid":17765,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T02:33:04.000Z","msg":"捐你老母閪咩捐"},{"pid":"c2fca642f57b42b067ce304fcc4451fd07ced161","tid":684851,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":7,"